high_descs: Head to the left of the oven
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and head to the counter to the right of the oven
Slice the loaf of bread into slices
Place the knife on the counter
Grab a slice of bread
Turn around and head to the microwave
Put the bread in the microwave and cook it. Grab the bread and close the microwave.
Turn left and stop at the trash can
Throw the bread in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Putting bread in a trash can

high_descs: Go to the counter next to the stove.
Pick up the butter knife next to the stove.
Go to the counter on the other side of the stove.
Slice the bread next to the toaster.
Set the butter knife down on the counter next to the stove.
Pick up a piece of bread.
Take the bread to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Take the warm bread to the trash can at the end of the counter.
Throw the warm bread in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw a warm piece of bread in the trash can.

high_descs: Walk straight turn to the right
Walk over to the counter
Pick the knife up from the counter
Back up and turn walk straight to the other counter
Take the knife and use it to cut a piece of bread
Pick the bread up and walk over to the microwave
Place the bread in the microwave
Turn the microwave on to heat the bread up
Take the bread out of the microwave
Carry the bread to other side of the kitchen
anns.task_desc: Cut a piece of bread and warm it up to get ready to eat
